The paper discusses many-task computing (MTC) in the context of the proposed Blue Waters system, which is a high-performance computing (HPC) system. Therefore, cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.HPC (High Performance Computing) are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the hardware and software requirements for MTC, which could fall under cs.OS (Operating Systems) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
